Josef! Show him
how to keep up his guard.

44
00:11:11,302 --> 00:11:13,755
Good... Come on, come on...

45
00:11:23,894 --> 00:11:26,836
What are you doing?
What's this, what's this?

46
00:11:28,286 --> 00:11:30,720
Watch your right,
