47
00:11:48,326 --> 00:11:49,955
That's it?

48
00:12:03,608 --> 00:12:07,426
I'm really sorry, father.
I didn't even recognize you.

49
00:12:07,845 --> 00:12:09,283
That's ok.

50
00:12:10,950 --> 00:12:13,691
We met during the strike?

51
00:12:14,876 --> 00:12:17,169
