72
00:13:39,937 --> 00:13:42,370
Well, I checked it out, I thought
you might give me this one.

73
00:13:42,502 --> 00:13:44,558
Did you go there with your
Solidarity friends?

74
00:13:48,974 --> 00:13:51,156
